    Copyright (c) 2025 GLK

The upstream MIT license is retained in `LICENSE`.

The financial temporal RAG track in this repository is a derived research
prototype. The added contribution includes the financial temporal graph schema,
FinFact extraction and retrieval modules, ECT-QA evaluation scripts, LLM judge
workflow, regression/ablation summaries, and project documentation.

External datasets, model providers, and APIs used when running this project may
have their own terms. In particular, ECT-QA data should be obtained from its
official source, and API credentials must be supplied locally through `.env`.
